dc_title_s: Map of the State of Florida, showing the progress of the surveys, accompanying annual report of the Surveyor General for 1856.
dc_description_s: Relief shown by hachures. "Approved October 1st, 1856, John Westcott, Surveyor General." "Sen. ex doc. no. 5 3rd sess. 34th Cong." 1 map; on sheet 71 x 67 cm.
